Book Tee Times
Special Events at Fernandina Beach
Fernandina Beach welcomes all types of special events — weddings, banquets, parties, meetings & more!
Numerous local businesses, organizations, clubs and private groups choose Fernandina Beach Golf Club as the host of their annual golf events. Regardless of whether your event is to raise funds or to raise spirits, we guarantee the satisfaction of your participants and guests. We make you and your guests feel at home, and promise to make your event an enjoyable and successful experience. To receive a personalized proposal for your wedding or banquet, please complete the form
here
to contact us directly.
View Our Banquet Menu
